Class GoldEntityAndAttributeReaderPipelineForSeedCorpus

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ctakes.assertion.pipelines.GoldEntityAndAttributeReaderPipelineForSeedCorpus

  • public class GoldEntityAndAttributeReaderPipelineForSeedCorpus
extends java.lang.Object
    A class for testing the reader for the gold standard relation data. Currently this class runs the reader and saves the resulting annotations as xmi files.
